  "detailed_description": "WTC 3 is the concluding chapter of the Welcome To... Chichester series.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.webp?t=1674246670\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras_big/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.avif?t=1674246670 width=800 height=63 /></span><br><br>The protagonist's final day of his/her holiday has finally arrived.  Despite being abducted by Grendel, it has been - <i>after the initial shock</i> - fun.<br>However, dark clouds are on the horizon, as Grendel reveals her final plan whilst two of the protagonist's enemies also make their moves.<br><br>Meanwhile, at The Phoenix Custodian's base, Lorinda believes the protagonist is about to betray her organisation.<br><br>Your final day has arrived.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.webp?t=1674246670\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras_big/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.avif?t=1674246670 width=800 height=63 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Funny and dramatic conclusion to the series</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.webp?t=1674246670\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras_big/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.avif?t=1674246670 width=800 height=63 /></span><br><br>Misericordia<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041660/extras/740cf034ff6e7cabcdf019ca2b042b94.avif?t=1674246670\" width=256 heigh